### FIFTY-SIX

The wise keep silent; a babbler is not wise. Keep your mouth closed and
guard the gates of sense. Hide

<span id="page_57">p. 57</span>

your sharpness, free yourself from entanglements, conceal your
personality, be socially minded and natural. Thus to harmonize one's
life with the life of others is the teh of the profound TAO.

No one can befriend such a man, nor can they estrange him, nor endanger
him, nor honor him, nor despise him. Such a man is naturally honored by
all the world.

